appstream: appstream (tools and libraries to work with AppStream metadata)
appstream:
appstream: AppStream is a collaborative effort for making machine-readable
appstream: software metadata easily available to programs that need it.
appstream: It is part of the Freedesktop ecosystem and provides a convenient
appstream: way to retrieve information about available software, making it
appstream: one of the building blocks for modern software centers.
appstream:
appstream:
appstream: See: https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Distributions/AppStream/
